# Documentation Rules

- Complex logic must include comments explaining *why*.
- Public functions and hooks should be documented.
- The project must have a README with:
  - Setup instructions
  - Architecture overview
  - Key decisions
- Each feature folder should contain a short README.
- New developers should understand a feature in under 10 minutes.
